 responsible for increasing supervisor and employee effectiveness through training and coaching programs, including building systems and processes to streamline workflow and increase company profits.\r\n\r\nMr. Boone has substantial experience in employee relations, including mediating employee disputes and resolving grievances. He has also developed supervisor and employee training programs to improve job effectiveness and prevent unlawful harassment. He also assists employers with drafting employee handbooks and job descriptions, and conducting effective employee evaluations. Mr. Boone is a member of the Society for Human Resource Management. He and his wife Kasey, a Clovis native, recently returned to the area with their three children.', 'Our Team', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '31-revision-5', '', '', '2009-03-05 06:39:13', '2009-03-05 14:39:13', '', 31, 'http://sierrahr.com/2009/03/31-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
