INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (216, 1, '2013-08-08 08:24:54', '2013-08-08 16:24:54', '<h2 style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><a rel="attachment wp-att-229" href="http://localhost:8080/test/logo-5/"></a>Specializing in Human Resource\nCompliance, Recruiting and Training</h2>\n<p style="text-align: left;">You are invited to attend our Sexual Harassment Prevention Training Seminar on Wednesday, August 24, 2011 from 9-11:15am. Please RSVP early as seats fill up quickly. To register, you may reply to Lauren Stefanopoulos at stefanopoulos@sierrahr.com, phone or fax in the registration slip below. We hope to see you there!</p>\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Sexual Harassment Prevention Training</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Mandatory for California Employers</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">With 50 or more employees.</p>\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left">We recommend all employers provide this training as a proactive step in improving morale and defending against potential lawsuits. AB 1825 requires employers with 50 or more employees to provide two hours of interactive sexual harassment prevention training to all supervisors every two years, effective January 1, 2006. In addition, new supervisors must be trained within six months of hire or promotion. Are you in compliance?</p>\n\nOur program, developed with lawyers, meets all AB 1825 requirements in a fun and interactive forum. Our certified HR professionals have over 20 years of training and compliance experience, and incorporate harassment examples based on actual workplace situations.\n\nDon’t wait until a complaint is filed. Fax or mail registration form below with your payment today!\n\n$69 per person (includes certification). Workshop Location: Sierra HR Partners, 7447 N. First Street, Suite 103, Fresno, CA 93720. For more information, please call 559.431.8090\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------