yment &amp; business reference verifications, professional license verifications, and social security number verifications. \r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><a rel="attachment wp-att-489" href="http://sierrahr.com/our-team/lauren-stefanopoulos/"></a><a rel="attachment wp-att-498" href="http://sierrahr.com/our-team/lauren-stefanopoulos-2/"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-498" title="Lauren Stefanopoulos" src="http://sierrahr.com/wp-content/uploads/Lauren-Stefanopoulos1-107x150.jpg" alt="Lauren Stefanopoulos" width="107" height="150" /></a>Lauren Stefanopoulos </h3>\r\nReceptionist/Administrative Assistant\r\n\r\nLauren Stefanopoulos is a graduate of California State University, Fresno.  She earned a Bachelor of Science degree in Business Administration with an emphasis in Human Resource Management.', 'Our Team', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '31-revision-75', '', '', '2011-11-30 10:04:27', '2011-11-30 18:04:27', '', 31, 'http://sierrahr.com/2011/11/31-revision-75/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
