learn more about some of the common myths and facts associated with the background check process please <a href="/background-investigations/myths-facts/?phpMyAdmin=8f0c4a1c5d31t4651115a">Click Here...</a>', 'Background Investigations', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-12', '', '', '2013-10-04 09:37:41', '2013-10-04 17:37:41', '', 19, 'http://localhost:8080/2013/10/19-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (742, 1, '2013-10-04 12:52:11', '2013-10-04 20:52:11', '<strong>Title: </strong>Behavior-Based Interviewing\r\n<strong>Location: </strong>FLGZ Law Office Conference Room 7112 N. Fresno St., Ste.450\r\n<strong>Description: </strong>Turnover is costly, time consuming and a downright hassle.  Employers can alleviate this burden by adopting a structured hiring process focused on behavior-based interviewing.  Join us to learn how to ask the right questions, get the answers you need and make informed hiring decisions.\r\n<strong>Start Time: </strong>09:00\r\n<strong>Date: </strong>2013-07-18\r\n<strong>End Time: </strong>12:00 Noon', 'Behavior-Based Interviewing', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '687-autosave', '', '', '2013-10-04 12:52:11', '2013-10-04 20:52:11', '', 687, 'http://localhost:8080/2013/10/687-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (743, 1, '2013-10-04 08:24:53', '2013-10-04 16:24:53', '<strong>Every year we review laws, regulations, and judicial opinions affecting California employers. By conducting this review we are able to implement revisions of your employee hand book and current policies to keep you in compliance with current state and federal employment laws.</strong>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Changes in 2013</span></h3>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Equal employment opportunity</li>\r\n	<li>Discrimination and harassment</li>\r\n	<li>Meal periods</li>\r\n	<li>Rest periods</li>\r\n	<li>Pregnancy and disability leave of absence</li>\r\n	<li>Sick leave</li>\r\n	<li>The use of social networking communications</li>\r\n	<li>Social media passwords</li>\r\n	<li>Commissioned employees</li>\r\n	<li>Access to your own personal records</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Labor Law Updates', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-9', '', '', '2013-10-04 08:24:53', '2013-10-04 16:24:53', '', 29, 'http://localhost:8080/2013/10/29-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (744, 1, '2009-03-04 18:39:38', '2009-03-05 02:39:38', '<p style="text-align: center;">We are privileged to work with fantastic clients, on challenging projects. Our staff is dedicated, skilled and conscientious. Our professionals are recognized as experts in their fields, and certified by the Human Resource Certification Institute. Together, we are committed to the following principles on which this firm was founded:</p>\r\n\r\n<em><strong>We will find, create and implement innovative solutions to the challenges facing our clients’ businesses.</strong></em> We will consider, evaluate and recommend solutions. We will work as a team and seek input from our network of professionals, including lawyers and other workplace experts.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>We will understand, respect and value our clients, their businesses and goals.</strong></em> We are committed to understanding our clients’ operations and the industries in which they compete. We will become well acquainted with the principals and members of the management teams and staff.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>We understand that there is always a better way to do business and we will always strive to improve our services.</strong></em> We won’t be satisfied with what we did yesterday. We recognize that circumstances change and industry conditions fluctuate. We will recognize those changes, anticipate future changes, and recommend action based on the most current information available.', 'Our Commitment to You', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-5', '', '', '2009-03-04 18:39:38', '2009-03-05 02:39:38', '', 12, 'http://localhost:8080/2009/03/12-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
