ily and friends, and participating in outdoor activities in all seasons.', ' Our Team', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '31-revision-138', '', '', '2015-01-26 14:15:40', '2015-01-26 22:15:40', '', 31, 'http://sierrahr.com/2015/01/31-revision-138/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
